                <text_1740702241
                    cq:styleIds="[1644862132301]"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;h1>Navigation&lt;sub>v2&lt;/sub>&lt;/h1>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <text
                    cq:styleIds="[1544762734201]"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>Navigation allows an author to build a site navigation. It is commonly added to a page template, in the header or footer.&lt;/p>&lt;p>When added to a page template, if the configured &lt;i>Navigation Root&lt;/i> is in a live copy blueprint or language copy master, then the navigation displayed on the pages resulting from this template will display the navigation structure that the accessed page is located in.&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <teaser
                    cq:styleIds="[1550165685463]"
                    jcr:description="&lt;p>GitHub&lt;/p>"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Technical Documentation"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/teaser"
                    actionsEnabled="false"
                    descriptionFromPage="false"
                    fileReference="/content/dam/core-components-examples/library/github-logo.svg"
                    linkURL="https://www.adobe.com/go/aem_cmp_tech_navigation_v2"
                    textIsRich="true"
                    titleFromPage="false"/>
                <teaser_556024830
                    cq:styleIds="[1550165685463]"
                    jcr:description="&lt;p>Adobe Help Center&lt;/p>"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Using Core Components"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/teaser"
                    actionsEnabled="false"
                    descriptionFromPage="false"
                    fileReference="/content/dam/core-components-examples/library/adobe-logo.svg"
                    linkURL="https://www.adobe.com/go/aem_cmp_navigation_v2"
                    textIsRich="true"
                    titleFromPage="false"/>
                <title_865328580
                    cq:styleIds="[1544759664489]"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Examples"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h2"/>
                <title_290384408
                    cq:styleIds="[1544759676459]"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Standard"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h3"/>
                <text_1337506761
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>The default behavior of the navigation component is to generate a nested navigation structure from the configured page tree. It will collect all child pages by iterating deeply through the entire page hiearchy. When not configured otherwise, the root page will be excluded, and all pages that are marked to be hidden from the navigation will not be listed. The text shown for each linked page is the &lt;i>Navigation Title&lt;/i> when provided by the page, or the main page &lt;i>Title&lt;/i> otherwise. Pages that have a redirection target to other pages, like the &lt;i>Breadcrumb&lt;/i> and the &lt;i>Language Navigation&lt;/i> pages will be linked directly to the redirection target, from which also the title is taken.&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <demo
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo">
                    <component
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/component">
                        <navigation
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/navigation"
                            navigationRoot="/content/core-components-examples/library"/>
                    </component>
                    <info
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/tabs">
                        <properties
                            cq:panelTitle="Properties"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/properties"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <markup
                            cq:panelTitle="Markup"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/markup"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <json
                            cq:panelTitle="JSON"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/json"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                    </info>
                </demo>
                <title_290386545
                    cq:styleIds="[1544759676459]"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Show Root Page"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h3"/>
                <text_1337509867
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>In this example we display the root page that is hidden by default by reducing the &lt;i>Exclude Root Levels&lt;i> option to zero.&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <demo_56474747
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo">
                    <component
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/component">
                        <navigation
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/navigation"
                            navigationRoot="/content/core-components-examples/library"
                            structureStart="0"/>
                    </component>
                    <info
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/tabs">
                        <properties
                            cq:panelTitle="Properties"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/properties"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <markup
                            cq:panelTitle="Markup"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/markup"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <json
                            cq:panelTitle="JSON"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/json"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                    </info>
                </demo_56474747>
                <title_2061144506
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Starting Level"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h3"/>
                <text_130342336
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>Multiple root levels can be skipped. In this example, setting the &lt;i>Exclude Root Levels&lt;/i> to 2 shows then only shows the leaf pages.&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <demo_1435920429
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo">
                    <component
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/component">
                        <navigation
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/navigation"
                            navigationRoot="/content/core-components-examples/library"
                            structureStart="2"/>
                    </component>
                    <info
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/tabs">
                        <properties
                            cq:panelTitle="Properties"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/properties"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <markup
                            cq:panelTitle="Markup"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/markup"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <json
                            cq:panelTitle="JSON"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/json"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                    </info>
                </demo_1435920429>
                <title
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Structure Depth"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h3"/>
                <text_894947512
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>By default, the navigation is lists all child pages. In this example, we disabling the option to &lt;i>Collect all child pages&lt;/i>, and then reduce &lt;i>Navigation Structure Depth&lt;/i> to the first level only.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <demo_650088868
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo">
                    <component
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/component">
                        <navigation
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/navigation"
                            navigationRoot="/content/core-components-examples/library"
                            collectAllPages="false"
                            structureDepth="1"/>
                    </component>
                    <info
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/tabs">
                        <properties
                            cq:panelTitle="Properties"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/properties"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <markup
                            cq:panelTitle="Markup"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/markup"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <json
                            cq:panelTitle="JSON"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/json"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                    </info>
                </demo_650088868>
                <title_2
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Disable Shadowing"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h3"/>
                <text_894947513
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>In the previous examples, notice how the &lt;i>Breadcrumb&lt;/i> and the &lt;i>Language Navigation&lt;/i> pages that redirect to a much deeper child page were linked directly to the target page. This allows authors to create menu structures that can be different from the actual page hierarchy.&lt;/p>&lt;p>The example below shows how that automatic linking to the target page can be disabled (listing only the templating section).&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <demo_650088869
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo">
                    <component
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/component">
                        <navigation
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/navigation"
                            navigationRoot="/content/core-components-examples/library/core-structure"
                            disableShadowing="true"/>
                    </component>
                    <info
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/tabs">
                        <properties
                            cq:panelTitle="Properties"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/properties"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <markup
                            cq:panelTitle="Markup"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/markup"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                        <json
                            cq:panelTitle="JSON"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/json"
                            reference="../../component"/>
                    </info>
                </demo_650088869>
                <title_30
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    jcr:title="Accessibility Landmark"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/title"
                    type="h3"/>
                <text_394947522
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>By default, the navigation component has a &lt;i>navigation&lt;/i> role applied. Authors can change this to a different value if desired, like below where a &lt;i>Secondary Navigation&lt;/i> role is set (listing only the templating section).&lt;/p>"
                    textIsRich="true"/>
                <demo_450088878
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo">
                    <component
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/demo/component">
                        <navigation
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/navigation"
                            navigationRoot="/content/core-components-examples/library/core-structure"
                            accessibilityLabel="Secondary Navigation"/>
                    </component>
                    <info
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
